children.label: Bottom Content
children.default:
Building Reading Success with Wiley Blevins, a module-based intervention program, provides systematic and explicit instruction with an embedded review and repetition cycle.

Meet students' needs with:

  • Flexible implementation models to address various instructional schedules and strategies
  • Innovative digital resources that engage students in active learning
  • Interactive assessments to determine placement and measure student progress
  • A transition Module to preclude decayed learning
